[00:31.81]"I knocked. 'Who is there?' said the old man. 'Come in.' 
“我敲了敲门，’谁啊？‘老人说，’请进！‘”

[00:37.93]"I entered. 'Pardon this intrusion,'I said;  'I am a traveller in want of a little rest; you would greatly oblige me if you would allow me to remain a few minutes before the fire.' 
